{"tid":904101,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【俾番嗰個曼玉我…】54歲張曼玉現身上海 宣佈今年出EP","createTime":"2018-11-16T05:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T02:37:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fdff0ef44fff1cfee07c30a2be443ada0af51e7c","tid":904101,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:16:39.000Z","msg":"54歲張曼玉，噚晚在上海出席活動，近年甚少現身嘅佢，成為全場焦點。而佢3、4年前出活動時，因為過瘦顯得有點憔悴，加上臉部紋路明顯而被指「變殘」。而且今次佢亮相時，頭髮剪短並染髮，臉頰仍顯得瘦削，但精神不錯，不過依然有台灣網民指佢跟75歲連戰夫人連方瑀神韻相似，網民感嘆歲月催人。<br />\n在活動紅地毯上，張曼玉透露最近工作計劃，忙於音樂方面，望今年可以出EP&hellip;咦，得番一個月左右咋喎。<br />\n其實張曼玉的演技是華人影壇傳奇，佢先後獲得康城同柏林影后，還有5次金馬影后及5次金像獎影后等多個影后殊榮。<br />\n但近年佢對音樂充滿熱誠，自從佢2004年拍前夫執導嘅電影《錯過又如何》後，開始接觸獨立音樂人，並在電影中演唱四首歌，此後佢開始用電腦軟件製作音樂，2012年佢曾與樂隊在北京首次公開現場獻唱。2014年張曼玉以搖滾歌手身份，獲邀在上海草莓音樂節中獻唱《甜蜜蜜》等，其低沉嗓音雖然遭到批評，不過佢始終有一顆搖滾心，2015年佢仲為電影《戀愛中的城市》創作兼主唱主題曲《如果沒了你》，仍在追音樂夢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181116/large/1542338957_0322.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181116%2Flarge%2F1542338957_0322.jpg&h=dcafedbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181116/large/1542338957_f463.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181116%2Flarge%2F1542338957_f463.jpg&h=3f3eb032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181116/large/1542338956_b3ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181116%2Flarge%2F1542338956_b3ae.jpg&h=35d7d7b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181116/large/1542340562_2f05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181116%2Flarge%2F1542340562_2f05.jpg&h=88f7e4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2014年張曼玉曾在活動上打碟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181116/58919576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F58919576&d=38jqZUFrbngVAerxXx0BOwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5fe8fd11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181116%2F58919576&h=1c72d9de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181116/58919576</a>"},{"pid":"867c6f458c3a74315d55551d762db67ae78ee7c6","tid":904101,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:18:16.000Z","msg":"甜..蜜....蜜........<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4903e9867179bfa184fbd9f64e37ed22ec5500","tid":904101,"uid":168366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"殺左個髮型師佢啦"},{"pid":"74e9368ce4c95f0edd91cc0c938bd40e9b2d26a9","tid":904101,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c4903e9867179bfa184fbd9f64e37ed22ec5500","tid":904101,"uid":168366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"殺左個髮型師佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:16:03.000Z","msg":"已經唔止個髮型事"},{"pid":"9ca4893f9fc5fdab63b16498361dae64086b5ac8","tid":904101,"uid":42064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:31:52.000Z","msg":"仲以為最尾嗰張係汪明荃"},{"pid":"b025aa796c01121a19e16c7ab8f7cb901f55a505","tid":904101,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"佢之前唱歌都好經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cbb820c06122039fe4952bd9168f6d597eb082","tid":904101,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"何方妖孽<img src